            "stanza_text": "LES miroirs de Murano\nDont la clarté peu commune\nEst prise aux rayons de lune,\nAux feux de pur diamant\nQue jette l'œil d'un amant,\nUn soir de bonne fortune."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Qu'une dame aux cheveux longs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sortant du bain, nue, exquise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Devant ce miroir soit mise.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
