                    "line_text": "Plus pur apparaît son corps,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dévoilant ses chauds accords",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Où la palette s'épuise.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'une dame aux cheveux longs.\nSortant du bain, nue, exquise,\nDevant ce miroir soit mise.\nPlus pur apparaît son corps,\nDévoilant ses chauds accords\nOù la palette s'épuise."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Mais ces miroirs ne sont rien",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Reine des flots, qui dans l'onde",
