                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "De tes marbres ouvragés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "De tes portiques légers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Où ton passé vagabonde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais ces miroirs ne sont rien\nReine des flots, qui dans l'onde\nPenches la couronne blonde\nDe tes marbres ouvragés,\nDe tes portiques légers\nOù ton passé vagabonde."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Dans la gondole au flanc noir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Couchés comme dans la tombe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "L'essaim de blancheur qui tombe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Pour se mirer dans les eaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Tous les amoureux oiseaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Désir, rêve, astre et colombe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans la gondole au flanc noir,\nCouchés comme dans la tombe.\nL'essaim de blancheur qui tombe\nPour se mirer dans les eaux.\nTous les amoureux oiseaux,\nDésir, rêve, astre et colombe."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Et tous deux glissons sans bruit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Pour nous aimer davantage,",
